OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,6,Fspells and increasingly strong
OL,7,Feasterly winds, with a chance of
OL,8,Fcoastal gales. Warm inland but cooler
OL,9,Falong eastern coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,12,Fsunny spells, though remaining windy.
OL,13,FA mostly clear night will follow,
OL,14,Fbecoming cool with a brisk breeze.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FAnother day of long sunny
OL,17,Fspells. Windy, though less so inland
OL,18,Fthan on Wednesday, with strongest
OL,19,Fwinds near coasts. Warm, but feeling
OL,20,Fcooler in exposed areas and along
OL,21,Feastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
